        "info": "The api-config node holds centralized settings:\n- Database connection (optional)\n- OAuth2/Keycloak settings (optional)\n- OPA policy settings (optional)\n- API versioning (/api/v1)\n- OpenAPI metadata\n- Logging configuration\n\nThe api-server node creates a Fastify HTTP server with:\n- OpenAPI specification endpoint (/openapi.json)\n- Swagger UI documentation (/docs)\n- Prometheus metrics (/metrics)",
