        "name": "CRUD Endpoints",
        "info": "Each api-endpoint node defines:\n- HTTP path and method\n- Request validation schemas (body, query, params)\n- Response schemas (for OpenAPI documentation)\n- CRUD operation type (list, get, create, update, delete)\n- Error handling configuration\n\nThe endpoint nodes connect to function nodes that handle the actual business logic.",
